id: pm-x7g1
title: GH #268-#270 agent lookup and context output polish
description: "Fix the small GitHub-reported agent UX bugs found during PR #266 audit: exact/short ID pm search should find items (#268), list-blocked should use the same compact projection as sibling list-status commands (#269), and pm context markdown metadata should not advertise a blockers section it does not render (#270). Duplicate check: pm search found no canonical open items for these exact GitHub issues; broader closed search/context work exists but not these open reports."
type: Task
status: closed
priority: 1
tags: []
created_at: "2026-06-18T00:09:30.023Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-18T00:40:14.928Z"
author: codex-audit-agent
parent: pm-mpbb
resolution: "Exact and short ID search now returns matching items, list-blocked defaults to the same compact status-list projection as sibling commands, and context markdown section metadata is limited to sections with rendered markdown bodies."
expected_result: GitHub #268-#270 should be resolved without expanding command verbosity or breaking existing list/search/context contracts.
actual_result: "Focused tests passed; manual temp-project dist/cli.js smoke confirmed id search, list-blocked compact projection, and context markdown section metadata behavior."
