  "2026-06-18T00:14:34.662Z",codex-audit-agent,"Evidence: fixed GitHub #268, #269, and #270. Manual temp-project check with dist/cli.js confirmed pm search <id> and short id return the matching item with matched_fields:[id], list-blocked --json uses projection.mode compact, and context --format markdown --depth deep no longer advertises an empty blockers section. Focused suite passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/commands/search-command.spec.ts tests/unit/commands/register-commands.spec.ts tests/unit/commands/context-command.spec.ts plus prior review/cleanup suites (8 files / 323 tests)."
